<!doctype html>
<html>
	<head>
		<title>The Glossary</title>
		<link href="assets/style.css" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css">
	</head>
	<body>
		<h1 class="title">The Glossary</h1>
		<dl class="glossary">
			{{#entries}}
			{{{render}}}
			{{/entries}}
		</dl>
		<h2 class="title">About</h2>
		<p>
			The Glossary is a dictionary of technical terms with plain definitions.
			It was started in frustration when I couldn't keep the difference between
			authorization and authentication straight in my head. As a result, they
			are the first two terms with a definition.
		</p>
		<p>
			To contribute, either by adding a definition, requesting a definition, or
			suggesting an alternate definition, make an issue or pull-request for this
			page's <a href="https://github.com/nuclearsandwich/glossary">GitHub Repo</a>.
			If that seems daunting to you, send an email to
			<a href="mailto:steven+glossary@nuclearsandwich.com">steven@nuclearsandwich.com</a>.
		</p>
		<p>
			All definitions are the sole copyright of their contributor and made
			made available under the Creative Commons Non-Commercial License.
		</p>
	</body>
</html>
